<headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 28 at 4:28AM EDT  by NWS Boston</headline>
<description>...PATCHY DENSE FOG EARLY THIS MORNING...
Patchy dense fog will reduce visibility to a quarter mile in some
locations early this morning. The fog will not be widespread but
motorists should be prepared for sudden changes in visibility. The
fog will lift by 8 or 9 am.</description>
